title: TD’s Bharadwaj Sees Dollar Erasing 2026 Loss With February Bump
description: The dollar is likely to extend its rebound this month in what is typically a strong part of the year for US economic data, according to Jayati Bharadwaj, a currency strategist at TD Securities.
